{"tid":897080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Navarro 警告高盛等華爾街金融機構，稱他們是「未登記的外國代理人」","createTime":"2018-11-10T15:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T09:51:48.000Z","uid":147314,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"40c70ea70766b8d05eee43e6091685e54869d341","tid":897080,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>鷹派白宮顧問警告華爾街勿插手美中貿易談判</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2018年11月10日 22:46 </span><br />\n白宮國家貿易委員會主席納瓦洛（Peter Navarro）警告高盛等華爾街金融機構，不要插手美中貿易談判，並稱他們是<span style=\"color: red;\">「未登記的外國代理人」（unregistered foreign agents）</span>，試圖向美國總統川普施壓，與大陸達成協議。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦洛上周五在華府智庫戰略與國際研究中心（CSIS）舉辦的活動，炮轟敦促美中結束貿易紛爭的華爾街現任和前任高階主管，企圖在本月底的20國集團 （G20）峰會舉行前，向白宮施壓。」<br />\n<br />\n納瓦洛嚴辭批評這些「支持全球主義的億萬富豪」，他說：「當這些沒有獲得報酬的外國代理人，從事這種所謂的外交時，他們這麼做只會削弱川普和他的談判地位，完全沒有好處。如果雙方達成協議，也會是美國總統川普的協議，不會是華爾街的協議。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181110002951-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181110002951-260408&d=5r1S28h%2BdlPdArFxc0HKittKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=cd0aaf4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181110002951-260408</a>"},{"pid":"7dd2544b09a6b9510969e5698b73939276a386c9","tid":897080,"uid":147314,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20181110/024241888717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20181110%2F024241888717.jpg&h=4082277e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477d798410d7d3765705a11a7f560ea0d98b965c","tid":897080,"uid":147314,"like":28,"dis