mal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得罪wall street果班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"佢自己都係老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6fca874120ac502cd162da664935453e001952","tid":897080,"uid":147314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:46:23.000Z","msg":"《外國代理人登記法》（Foreign Agents Registration Act，簡稱FARA）1938年通過，當時的目的是為了抵禦納粹德國的宣傳攻勢，要求代理「外國委託人」的任何個人或組織必須向美國司法部註冊並披露其代理的委託人身份，包括政府、政黨、美國以外的個人或組織。<br />\n<br />\n這部法律要求外國代理人每六個月向美國司法部提交有關代理人與外國委託人之間的合約、收款、支出的材料，如果該代理人出席國會作證，必須提供最近的登記聲明。法案還要求代理人保存所有活動記錄，並允許司法部長對其審查。<br />\n<br />\n法律要求，那些為外國委託人散播信息材料的登記者必須在宣傳材料上醒目標註外國委託人的身份，並說明該機構代表這一外國委託人在美國傳播這一材料。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部說，充當代理人的外國媒體機構必須在其網站首頁或「關於我們」的頁面醒目註明這一信息；在其臉書、推特等社交媒體、網上論壇和博客上，也應注明這一說明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-may-require-chinese-media-register-as-agents-20171117/4126255.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-may-require-chinese-media-register-as-agents-20171117%2F4126255.html&d=5r1S28h%2BdlPdArFxc0HKittKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2041844a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-may-require-chinese-media-register-as-agents-20171117/4126255.html</a>"},{"pid":"62d28c173666ac31988f951ac2f672a5b86011f6","tid":897080,"uid":14449,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77d9be60c1f53f1b8458725beb6d1c095cfc4a6e","tid":897080,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8960528ced326e9f86281509c10b85240d86d13","tid":897080,"uid":14449,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"侵侵會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得罪wall street果班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"佢自己都係老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"但都唔夠佢地有錢<br />\n高盛果班玩家買起成個國家都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05616e51894dec27b626130cd9104332c0cd6409","tid":897080,"uid":19527,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"62d28c173666ac31988f951ac2f672a5b86011f6","tid":897080,"uid":14449,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77d9be60c1f53f1b8458725beb6d1c095cfc4a6e","tid":897080,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8960528ced326e9f86281509c10b85240d86d13","tid":897080,"uid":14449,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"侵侵會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得罪wall street果班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"佢自己都係老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"但都唔夠佢地有錢<br />\n高盛果班玩家買起成個國家都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"買起啲馬來西亞果啲就得<br />\n買起美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d5061b931736b89a37dc0114ac45e8ea57f7ba","tid":897080,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y40mfQ8ygpQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY40mfQ8ygpQ&d=5r1S28h%2BdlPdArFxc0HKittKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=712f1ad7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y40mfQ8ygpQ</a>"},{"pid":"2b9fe28baa6b72e5b72659b140a475b0b736e3a4","tid":897080,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor